cal-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[20231105游资课上午-part003] <\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">分时交易细节<\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">：重点关注分时均线（VWAP）的支撑与压力。股价在VWAP上方震荡代表多头主导，跌破且反抽无力则为当日转弱信号。<\/span>","text":"[20231105游资课上午-part003] 分时交易细节：重点关注分时均线（VWAP）的支撑与压力。股价在VWAP上方震荡代表多头主导，跌破且反抽无力则为当日转弱信号。","isChecked":false},{"textHtml":"<span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[20231105游资课上午-part003] <\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">仓位对冲标准<\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">：在情绪不确定性增加时，应通过分批建仓或在不同位阶标的间进行仓位分配，以平滑净值波动。<\/span>","text":"[20231105游资课上午-part003] 仓位对冲标准：在情绪不确定性增加时，应通过分批建仓或在不同位阶标的间进行仓位分配，以平滑净值波动。","isChecked":false},{"textHtml":"<span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">[20231105游资课上午-获利战法] <\/span><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;